The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, specifically in the area of reading comprehension. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks, which suggests that it could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of large datasets, which could place it under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions the use of natural language derivations, which could suggest a connection to computer vision and image processing, placing it under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
